Title : Mauno Forsman
Text : '''Mauno Veikko Forsman''' (1928-2006) was a Finnish politician ([[Social Democratic Party of Finland|Social Democrat]]), Member of Parliament 1971-1983<ref name=riksdagen>{{cite web|url=http://www.eduskunta.fi/triphome/bin/hex5000.sh?hnro=910017&kieli=ru|title=Mauno Forsman|publisher=Parliament of Finland|accessdate=28 April 2014}}</ref> He was a deputy Minister of Finance 1981-1982.<ref name=riksdagen/>

From 1983â€“1987 he was the chairman of [[Finland's Bandy Association]].

